item.title: First Meeting 2023
item.description: TL;DR: When Where Link 2/10, 5:30pm MT TBD here Further Detail Our first meeting this semester will be Friday the 10th at 5:30pm at this link for remote members. Not discord. Physical location is not yet set, but will default to UCC 107. I’d like to find a room with a mic that can pick up in person members better, as that was a recurring issue last semester.
